snippet.title: Great Naval Battles 4 gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Great Naval Battles 4 (aka great naval battles vol. iv: burning steel, 1939-1942), Dos PC game produced by SSI in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/great-naval-battles-4/1582/
Playing through a random scenario in this naval warfare simulation. Showing most important features like navigation and surface attack.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:

Grandest Fleet, The - https://youtu.be/VOvRhclqGbk
Armored Fist - https://youtu.be/e_1BIW7Q_8Q
